looping: 

 - a condition has to be met in order for loop to exit 
 
 - while/until statements: conditional statements 
 
 - infinite loops - stopped by ctrl + c 
 
 
 - while (condition) 
    keep executing logic 
    
- until (condition) 
    keep executing logic 
    
    
  number = 0 
  
  while number < 5 
    the number is ... 
    
  end
  
  until number == 5 
    the number is #{number}
    number +=1
  end 